        "title": "What Is WeChat? A Deep Dive into How China's Super App Works, Why It Exists, and What the World Can Learn From It",
        "seo_title": "What Is WeChat? How China's Super App Works – Complete Educational Guide 2026",
        "slug": "what-is-wechat-how-chinas-super-app-works",
        "date": "Jun 22, 2026",
